      "para_id": "Q001490.1",
      "line_range": "1",
      "translation": "(1) For Ninĝirsu , the powerful warrior of Enlil , his master , Gudea , ruler of Lagaš , made an eternal thing appear : he built his E-ninnu-anzud-babbar , ( and ) built his beloved divine audience chamber from fragrant cedarwood inside it ."
    }
  ],
